  "prompt": "What are the best Hindi songs to sing?",
  "response": "Choosing the best Hindi songs to sing can depend on your personal taste, vocal range, and the occasion. Whether you're preparing for a karaoke night, a performance, or just singing for fun, here's a diverse list of popular and evergreen Hindi songs that are great choices:\n\n### **1. Classic Hits**\n- **\"Lag Ja Gale\"** \u2013 Lata Mangeshkar\n- **\"Pal Pal Dil Ke Paas\"** \u2013 Kishore Kumar\n- **\"Tujh Mein Rab Dikhta Hai\"** \u2013 Roop Kumar Rathod\n- **\"Pyaar Hua Ikrar Hua\"** \u2013 Manna Dey & Lata Mangeshkar\n- **\"Kya Hua Tera Wada\"** \u2013 Mohammed Rafi\n\n### **2. Romantic Songs**\n- **\"Tum Hi Ho\"** \u2013 Arijit Singh\n- **\"Pehla Nasha\"** \u2013 Udit Narayan & Sadhana Sargam\n- **\"Raabta\"** \u2013 Arijit Singh\n- **\"Tera Ban Jaunga\"** \u2013 Akhil Sachdeva & Tulsi Kumar\n- **\"Kalank Title Track\"** \u2013 Arijit Singh\n\n### **3. Upbeat and Party Songs**\n- **\"Gallan Goodiyaan\"** \u2013 Yashita Sharma, Farhan Akhtar & others\n- **\"Badtameez Dil\"** \u2013 Benny Dayal\n- **\"London Thumakda\"** \u2013 Labh Janjua, Sonu Kakkar & Neha Kakkar\n- **\"Desi Girl\"** \u2013 Vishal Dadlani, Amit Mishra & Shilpa Rao\n- **\"Swag Se Swagat\"** \u2013 Vishal Dadlani & Neha Bhasin\n\n### **4. Sad & Emotional Songs**\n- **\"Channa Mereya\"** \u2013 Arijit Singh\n- **\"Tujhe Kitna Chahne Lage\"** \u2013 Arijit Singh\n- **\"Jab Tak\"** \u2013 Armaan Malik\n- **\"Agar Tum Saath Ho\"** \u2013 Alka Yagnik & Arijit Singh\n- **\"Bhula Dena\"** \u2013 Mustafa Zahid\n\n### **5. Devotional Songs**\n- **\"Om Jai Jagdish Hare\"** \u2013 Traditional Devotional\n- **\"Shree Ganeshaya Dheemahi\"** \u2013 Traditional\n- **\"Rahe Teri\"** \u2013 Kailash Kher\n\n### **6. Old Bollywood Favorites**\n- **\"Mere Sapno Ki Rani\"** \u2013 Kishore Kumar\n- **\"Ye Sham Mastani\"** \u2013 Kishore Kumar\n- **\"Kahin Door Jab Din Dhal Jaye\"** \u2013 Mukesh\n- **\"Chura Liya Hai Tumne\"** \u2013 Asha Bhosle & Mohammed Rafi\n- **\"Ajeeb Dastan Hai Yeh\"** \u2013 Lata Mangeshkar\n\n### **7. Contemporary Hits**\n- **\"Shayad\"** \u2013 Arijit Singh\n- **\"Dil Diyan Gallan\"** \u2013 Atif Aslam\n- **\"Apna Time Aayega\"** \u2013 Ranveer Singh\n- **\"Ve Maahi\"** \u2013 Arijit Singh & Asees Kaur\n- **\"Raataan Lambiyan\"** \u2013 Jubin Nautiyal & Asees Kaur\n\n### **8. Folk and Regional Hits**\n- **\"Madhaniya\"** \u2013 Neha Bhasin\n- **\"Teri Mitti\"** \u2013 B Praak\n- **\"Mere Rashke Qamar\"** \u2013 Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan & Rahat Fateh Ali Khan\n\n### **Tips for Choosing the Right Song:**\n- **Vocal Range:** Select songs that suit your vocal strengths and range.\n- **Language & Pronunciation:** Ensure you're comfortable with the pronunciation and nuances of the lyrics.\n- **Emotional Connection:** Choose songs that resonate with you emotionally, as this can enhance your performance.\n- **Practice:** Some songs may require more practice due to complex melodies or fast-paced lyrics.\n\nRemember, the best song to sing is one that you enjoy and feel confident performing. Happy singing!",
